15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. From the funds appropriated to the Department of
17 Mental Health and Substance Abuse Services in Enrolled House Bill
18 No. 2766 of the 1st Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, the
19 sum of Ten Million Eight Hundred Twelve Thousand Four Hundred Eight
20 Dollars ($10,812,408.00) shall be used for program growth and to
21 replace funding no longer available due to the reduction of federal
22 matching dollars.
23 SECTION 2. From the funds appropriated to the Department of
24 Mental Health and Substance Abuse Services in Enrolled House Bill
